{
  "stem": "23832.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, and I came there, and I thought the girl wouldn't know anything.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was smart to bribe her.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I took off of me a set of very expensive underwear-- satin, very expensive.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, like, decorated with satin and very expensive.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't see them now.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They don't have them here.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I gave her.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I said, Miss Polcja-- called her her name.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I said, I'm so hungry.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] So I had to give her some change and she went and bought me a roll and a milk.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then I say, and I didn't wash for a long time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I said, Miss Polcja, I need to get a shower.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And she said, lady, hose behind the walls.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I thought she doesn't know, but she was-- I couldn't fool her.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I fooled myself.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And so she let me take a shower and she let me to sleep in the boy's crib.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Now, the boy and the mother, which is the nurse, she was that time out in the countryside somewheres.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And that boyfriend husband, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] he used to work for the Germans, like, he was a truck-- he drove their truck.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And he would hide, under the engine or wherever, whatever he could buy there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He would buy sausage.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "He would buy all kinds of things and he brought.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But they-- he wouldn't come to-- and they communicated.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "When he brought the stuff, he called her from that little grocery store-- Papa-Mama grocery store.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "He called her and she would come and take that which he brought.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
